title: Buck Rogers
actors: Buster Crabbe, Constance Moore, Jackie Moran, Jack Mulhall, Anthony Warde, Philson Ahn, C. Montague Shaw, Guy Usher, William Gould, Henry Brandon, Wheeler Oakman, Kenne Duncan, Carleton Young, Reed Howes
description: A 20th Century pilot named Buck Rogers and his young friend Buddy Wade awake from 500 years in suspended animation to find that the world has been taken over by the outlaw army of Killer Kane.

title: Love Exposure
actors: Takahiro Nishijima, Hikari Mitsushima, Sakura Andô, Yutaka Shimizu, Makiko Watanabe, Hiroyuki Onoue, Atsuro Watabe, Tasuku Nagaoka, Sô Hirosawa, Yûko Genkaku, Mami Nakamura, Arata Yamanaka, Junya Iwamoto, Motoki Ochiai, Sango
description: A bizarre love triangle forms between a young Catholic upskirt photographer, a misandric girl and a manipulative cultist.
